### ========== AUTH ==========

### register attacker
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "attacker",
  "email": "attacker@test.com",
  "password": "parola123",
  "cityName": "Athens"
}

###

### register defender
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "defender",
  "email": "defender@test.com",
  "password": "parola123",
  "cityName": "Sparta"
}

###

### login attacker
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "attacker",
  "password": "parola123"
}

###

### login defender
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "defender",
  "password": "parola123"
}

